{"tid":760462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭鼓勵年輕人畢業後加入紀律部隊","createTime":"2018-07-29T14:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T01:07:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"29bf3112afb77c0fbc480ec86bbc8463d6b7f174","tid":760462,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T14:10:18.000Z","msg":"香港青少年軍事夏令營今舉行結業禮，特首林鄭月娥致辭時，寄語在場學員要訂定清晰的學習目標，積極為自己增值，又鼓勵他們在畢業後加入紀律部隊，為香港的未來作出貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指，國家發展迅速，「一帶一路」及粵港澳大灣區等政策，將為香港帶來種種機遇，強調「機會總是留給有準備的人」，籲年輕人及早裝備自己。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，青年工作是現屆政府的重要施政之一，而她非常支持香港青少年軍事夏令營，認為活動為香港學生提供了寶貴的學習經驗，讓他們親身體驗駐港部隊的生活，並鍛鍊體魄，培養領袖才能，以及刻苦、自律、守紀和團結的精神。<br />\n<br />\n全國政協副主席董建華、中聯辦主任王志民、外交部駐港特派員謝鋒及多名司局長亦有出席典禮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2125445/林鄭鼓勵年輕人畢業後加入紀律部隊\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2125445%2F%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E9%BC%93%E5%8B%B5%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E5%BE%8C%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5%E7%B4%80%E5%BE%8B%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A&d=BVLY2Jx7JIkSF0MxOOUexjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5266341e\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2125445/林鄭鼓勵年輕人畢業後加入紀律部隊</a>"},{"pid":"28a0748b28a6debe1151001bb2c1d7028911d958","tid":760462,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28eb219d7820cf1226f87d29d07d1b67704fed65","tid":760462,"uid":164913,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:04:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc6cc4acd6581115723cf8cabf6cf59703b15b59","tid":760462,"uid":102179,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:15:19.000Z","msg":"即刻話紀律部隊以外都係對社會冇貢獻既廢物<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692488274d8f98768bec7ada9e1e2a074be90780","tid":760462,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:34:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c2afdc0a70588ade457219f477b29e0b6b6ca9d","tid":760462,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T23:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://sites.google.com/site/pesickaenglish8students/_/rsrc/1362067936593/welcome/hitler-youth/5_07_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fsite%2Fpesickaenglish8students%2F_%2Frsrc%2F1362067936593%2Fwelcome%2Fhitler-youth%2F5_07_1.jpg&h=2555079c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啫係納粹青年軍"},{"pid":"2db17286c79ed86f5ac9ceded6853f7910667b42","tid":760462,"uid":109983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T23:35:49.000Z","msg":"加再次人工即入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f22768ea21f4242e10d41b293096a4508d4551","tid":760462,"uid":23162,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T23:48:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/091215_96d9bc19a70addbbc1056484a8006683.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F091215_96d9bc19a70addbbc1056484a8006683.png&h=19174810&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>香港警察</strong><br />\n各國警隊模範，正義感強大，效忠法律，是個不折不扣的硬漢。以往從未失手，罪案率每年創新低，專業廉潔，服務為本。然而，在兩年前各同袍與旺角暴徒交手時，慘遭陷害，乃至傷亡慘重，及不斷受到被蒙蔽的市民指責，但仍振作起來繼續與惡勢力作戰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/091232_e682bc4deb87cb05f885f627debc2e91.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F091232_e682bc4deb87cb05f885f627debc2e91.png&h=d28f8b68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>暴徒</strong><br />\n各懷技能，有IT仔、前軍人、武術家同上流人士等，受社會栽培但不報效社會。然而被對警察有敵意的人（即被拉過的罪犯）的流言影響，因此對警察恨之入骨。屢犯大案以民主作籍口，實際上卻是以獵殺警察為快樂，這次將港獨視為最大目標。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/091248_9b4d15a1997bb68fdd2cf84f065d7ddc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F091248_9b4d15a1997bb68fdd2cf84f065d7ddc.png&h=7c12b3fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>藍絲帶</strong><br />\n香港警察的支持者，平時受過警察無私的救助加上獨立思考，此後對警察懷有感激和崇拜。由於家庭背景而不做警察，卻整天渴望維護正義，於是開始扶持市民從陰霾裏清醒。雖然頭腦簡單，經常受到陷害及恥笑，但寧死不屈的拼搏精神，堅持心中的正義。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母臭化閪，其實你條柒頭貼啲咁嘢出嚟打飛機會射得順暢啲咩？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陽萎就做返啲正常人做嘅嘢啦懵撚。直頭好似啲痴漢除褲俾女睇咁撚肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7b3b40df2106c569e5bb320cd0145f3966c3eb","tid":760462,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:05:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf462a8109c6e7a5a83b624dbb0d0cb770fe6014","tid":760462,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:07:01.000Z","msg":"打柒刁民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}